{"tid":718363,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"茶盅泡茶","createTime":"2018-06-26T17:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T01:01:16.000Z","uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"15a8bea22546bb4adba76e90414a4e218b9f8fdc","tid":718363,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:33:22.000Z","msg":"一直以來都唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去蓮香樓飲茶就畀人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就喺屋企練緊點用<br />\n而家克服到燙手問題<br />\n手指擺位亦自問正確<br />\n但點倒茶都好 都總係多少滴咗啲喺檯面<br />\n我應該點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bb6d4b5d34fafb6489836aa172500236ecb17f","tid":718363,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T18:07:09.000Z","msg":"去返普通酒樓飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b3c308c974da12fcdde6e3041e7a69c1261faa","tid":718363,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T23:45:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4cc94ea8fc4efb0c8247e277db7f7aa1051500fe","tid":718363,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5b3c308c974da12fcdde6e3041e7a69c1261faa","tid":718363,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T23:45:00.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:35:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cbd9611aefc35879a0f03fc12f0f578c97721a67","tid":718363,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:36:27.000Z","msg":"天下武功，唯快不破"},{"pid":"2f65321124268ab940195ecd6f5567b8ee1bdeec","tid":718363,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd9611aefc35879a0f03fc12f0f578c97721a67","tid":718363,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:36:27.000Z","msg":"天下武功，唯快不破"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"克服恐懼真係最關鍵<br />\n心裡面提自己 幾燙手都面揸撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但倒茶嘅動作仍然未夠俐落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f9f1c96ef94d7b0a748af44b541a5d30762d91","tid":718363,"uid":47674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T02:07:48.000Z","msg":"我就好似呢張相咁<br />\n檯面總係有氹水<br />\n睇落武藝未精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imagejoy.com/images/articles4/337-lin-heung-tea-house-05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imagejoy.com%2Fimages%2Farticles4%2F337-lin-heung-tea-house-05.jpg&h=7b3d641d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76c0bad6c19e5d090a72a7d55438843b29ecc261","tid":718363,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"連登仔後生 冇人用茶盅呢啲阿叔玩意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a85f4a54ff756164ff82192fe4d2c9d1b20b2b","tid":718363,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:57:34.000Z","msg":"茶盅先正<br />\n想飲先加水<br />\n避免茶葉過度浸泡"},{"pid":"70a400e5055acbdef291b874c466ab1958000535","tid":718363,"uid":49620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd9611aefc35879a0f03fc12f0f578c97721a67","tid":718363,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T00:36:27.000Z","msg":"天下武功，唯快不破"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係快手啲就可以"},{"pid":"43a0b69fcb216083299b82c28f69a0b4c272b9e5","tid":718363,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96a85f4a54ff756164ff82192fe4d2c9d1b20b2b","tid":718363,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:57:34.000Z","msg":"茶盅先正<br />\n想飲先加水<br />\n避免茶葉過度浸泡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T02:08:05.000Z","msg":"燙手唔敢倒咪一樣過度浸泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9b63fba4fe1c3a5