ve%2Fq_auto%2Ff_auto%2Fbloghk%2F2017%2F09%2Fcaption.jpg&h=451d0c25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac6471a904841ad6de967024693f3fc8fd34abc0","tid":718363,"uid":5846,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"879f79a2f5de0492270c40e2e570c23bc6c43578","tid":718363,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"5e8f2e437a612878e4e73b1bcd01de7ccdf14881","tid":718363,"uid":5846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"淨係去蓮香樓飲茶都抵俾人笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又污糟又唔好食，態度又唔好<br />\n<br />\n求其一間都好過佢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"啲點心好懷舊好正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬拉糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/fl_lossy.progressive/q_auto/f_auto/bloghk/2017/09/caption.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.klook.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Ffl_lossy.progressive%2Fq_auto%2Ff_auto%2Fbloghk%2F2017%2F09%2Fcaption.jpg&h=451d0c25&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T23:46:50.000Z","msg":"淨係去過一次上環店 <br />\n<br />\n好少有茶樓令我覺得永不錄用，請都唔想去食。<br />\n<br />\n其實環境殘舊我預左。<br />\n<br />\n不過衛生絕對係我近幾年食過最衰嘅一間。<br />\n<br />\n但連枱布都無，上手客食完啲骨求其揾個布掃走就算，啲汁仲痴住張枱。我揾張濕紙一抹就成張黃晒，極想嘔，手機都完全唔敢放枱。<br />\n<br />\n價錢黎講，雖然唔算貴，不過以質素黎講根本唔算抵食，一分錢一分貨。中西 區黎講要揾好食過佢嘅大有店在。"},{"pid":"66726ce84650e7df79a967e24504576c82d1fa13","tid":718363,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a0c7ee95c0a4a38c109984cb270792dd97b65135","tid":718363,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"開口位自己就架啫<br />\n整細啲個開口位先再攞上手倒"},{"pid":"955b008df056bc9043a6ad9ea9fa233290caa9ef","tid":718363,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66726ce84650e7df79a967e24504576c82d1fa13","tid":718363,"uid":1567,"l